{"title":"元旦四绝","authors":["黄炎培"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":1,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"元旦四绝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄炎培"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年一月内战松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年战火北西东。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天干不见雪花白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但见血花满地红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年一月政协开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年决议烧了灰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借问将军马歇尔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“将军究为何事来”？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年陪都度新正，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年首都谒先灵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先灵地下惟痛哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭了民权哭民生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年战后呼苦恼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年舆论换一套："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“居不得安食不饱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死去还比活着好”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（转载自元旦文汇报）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}